{"id":470,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":72,"title":"72. On the Phone","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone.470/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/0-72-on-the-phone.mp3","transcript":"Good morning, Scott and Smith Law Office. May I help you?\nYes. May I speak to David Waller, please?\nI'm sorry, he isn't here yet. May I take a message?\nYes. Could you ask him to call Marjorie Vale?\nHow do you spell your last name?\nV-A-L-E.\nWhat's your phone number? Does Mr. Waller have it?\nUh, no, he doesn't.\nIt's 680-5290.\nI'm sorry, could you repeat that?\n680-5290.\nI'll give him the message.\nThank you.\nYou're welcome.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:59","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Good morning, Scott and Smith Law Office. May I help you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/1.mp3","time_start":2.28,"time_end":5.36},{"position":2,"content":"Yes. May I speak to David Waller, please?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/2.mp3","time_start":5.36,"time_end":7.78},{"position":3,"content":"I'm sorry, he isn't here yet. May I take a message?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/3.mp3","time_start":7.78,"time_end":10.84},{"position":4,"content":"Yes. Could you ask him to call Marjorie Vale?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/4.mp3","time_start":10.84,"time_end":14.02},{"position":5,"content":"How do you spell your last name?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/72-on-the-phone-2022-03-07-21-28-20/5.mp3","time_start":1